---
title: Sesame Crumbed Pork Schnitzel with Korean Stir-Fried Veggies & Garlic Aioli
description: Stir-fried veggies get a special touch when they're infused with our umami-packed Korean stir-fry sauce. It’s the perfect base for crumbed pork and aioli so you can taste a home-cooked Asian-fusion feast with ease!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
